last_episode_to_air.name: One Love
last_episode_to_air.overview: Ariana’s main source of inspiration is her fans. That’s why, after the Manchester terror attack, she decided to put together the One Love concert and resume her tour... as a show of love for her fans.

name: Ariana Grande: Dangerous Woman Diaries
overview: A behind the scenes look at Ariana Grande’s Dangerous Woman Tour and the making of Sweetener and music video from “the light is coming” and “God is a woman”.

episodes.name: the light is coming
episodes.overview: Ariana gives us a behind-the-scenes look at her work on her newest album, Sweetener, which is largely an artistic reaction to her experiences on the Dangerous Woman Tour.

episodes.name: Here's The Gag
episodes.overview: Ariana kicks off the Dangerous Woman Tour with her dancers and crew. We get insight into her creative process, her reasons for doing this series, and her relationship with the twins, Brian and Scott, her main collaborators.

episodes.name: Grateful
episodes.overview: Life on tour can be difficult, so Ariana shares how she and her crew cope while on the road. Also featuring never before seen footage of Ariana and her crew’s backstage antics.

episodes.name: One Love
episodes.overview: Ariana’s main source of inspiration is her fans. That’s why, after the Manchester terror attack, she decided to put together the One Love concert and resume her tour... as a show of love for her fans.
